OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Workplaces told to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fplan for absences of up to 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F25%                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have been tasked with        
OL,6, developing "robust contingency plans"  
OL,7, for workplace absences, as the         
OL,8, government warned rising cases could   
OL,9, see up to a quarter of staff off work. 
OL,11,FPublic sector leaders have been asked  
OL,12,Fto prepare for "worst case scenarios"  
OL,13,Fof 10%, 20% and 25% absence rates, the 
OL,14,FCabinet Office said.                   
OL,16,FThe UK has seen record numbers of daily
OL,17,Fcases over the festive period.         
OL,19,FTransport, the NHS and schools have    
OL,20,Falready seen the effect of absences.   
